{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 61.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as Hungarian Jews, we're entitled to better treatment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are Hungarian Jews-- like the Hungarian Jews, they were very proud Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were proud citizens of Hungary, like the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But A stands for 200,000.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was the prisoner-- by the way, only those prisoners that remain in Auschwitz were numbered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was prisoner 211,832.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was my number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from there I was marched to Auschwitz-- from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they lined us up on a-- on a-- you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were driving us, they were driving us to Auschwitz which is the camp in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when I saw the sign there [SPEAKING GERMAN], I'll never forget, never forget.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We came into that gate, and then we made a right turn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I see the sign, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I speak Yiddish, I said, oh, if you work, you're going to-- you know, whatever it means.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I felt a little better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They lined us up one day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And everybody-- we all have our shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they took off our shoes, and they pulled off the heels from the shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They pulled off the heels.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because some people put in money into the heels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they pulled off the heels from the shoes, and then they gave me other shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They gave me shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The shoes had wooden-- wooden soles with material on it, you know so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from there I was marched to a camp which is called Buna, Buna Monowitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Today, Auschwitz is called Auschwitz-I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Birkenau is called Auschwitz-II, and Buna is called Auschwitz-III.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Buna Monowitz one of it was a big factory which was an IG farm, IG farm from IG farm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they employed us as slave labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
